714754f-a.title: Manhattan: 88th Street (East) - York Avenue
714754f-a.text:
422-434 East 88th Street, south side, between York and First Aves.
showing the 35th Precinct Police Station. Today this structure is occupied
by a clinic of Metropolitan Hospital.
About 1910.

724915f-a.title: Manhattan: York Avenue - 88th Street
724915f-a.text:
York Avenue (Avenue A), east side, from 88th Street to and including
89th Street, showing one of the buildings of the House of the Good
Shepherd, on the N.W. corner of 89th Street. These houses antedate
1891.
January 31, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
